the elections to the assembly based in strasbourg france of 
the european economic community will be the second for spain since 
it joined the 12nation trading bloc in january 1986 
the first elections held june 10 1987 coincided with city and 
regional polls of the 60 seats alloted spain in the assembly 
gonzalezs ruling socialist party won 28 the largest conservative 
party popular alliance now the popular party won 17 and the 
centrist democratic social center won seven 
