georgia smaller than south carolina also was once an 
independent nation in 19181921 but russian troops were sent in 
and it was absorbed into the soviet union 
under soviet power georgians have thrived economically because 
the areas warm climate is ideally suited for resorts and growing 
the fruits and vegetables that are scarce elsewhere in the country 
but under leonid i brezhnev ethnic mafias ran the republic 
embezzlement cronyism and bribery were widespread black 
marketeering of farm produce was rampant 
before gorbachev named him foreign minister in 1985 eduard a 
shevardnadze an ethnic georgian served 13 years as the republics 
