stalins reign of terror the ethnic groups kept silent but 
gorbachevs policies of glasnost or openness and 
perestroika or restructuring have unleashed a torrent of 
complaints from the national groups 
basic nationalities problems have been swept under the rug for 
50 to 60 years now theyre authorities paying for it suny 
said 
gorbachevs liberalization has gone so far he said that the 
